				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><strong>Our Process</strong><br /><strong>Step-1</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Research and Discovery<br /><strong>Step-2</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Analysis<br /><strong>Step-3</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Plan and Strategize<br /><strong>Step-4</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Execution<br /><strong>Step-5</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Monitoring and Reporting<br /><strong>Step-6</strong> <img decoding="async" class="emoji" role="img" draggable="false" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/27a1.svg" alt="➡️" /> Leverage Opportunities.</p>								</div>
